text: And swa up on land scare hangran.
Þonne bi eastan cester slæd byrg.
XXX gerda swæ up to here paþe.
Þæt swa uest on here paþe anlang hrygges þæt of here paþe on rugan dic.
On ber hulle westewearde þonne forð ofer here pað þæt on sticelan pað on wadding gerstun easte weardne.
Þæt forð ofer chealf hylle middewearde þonne on wulfcumb ufeweardne swa ðurh dellwuda on landscoraac.
Swa of dune on stream þat up of streame on hanan welle.
